channel.title: Can't login? Any Ideas?
channel.description:
Hey sorry to bother everyone but im having trouble with my 525 server. It is CodeUsa and i can't get the client to load on my ip. If i set it to 127.0.0.1 it works fine but as soon as i set it to mine is Class68_sub20_sub15 it get the error error_game_js5connect. I have opened up the port through my router and set it to port 43594. I have went through all the stuff in no-ip this isn't my first server. But for some reason no matter what i do on a 525 i can't seem to get any of them to load. I always get the same error. I have followed a few tutorials and none work. Can anyone think of a quick reason why it isn't working? It is pretty frustrating because i have spent a lot of time on this server and the fact that i can't change my ip is pretty stupid.Thanks for your time=) :)
~Virgil~ Looking for a good tutorial on running 525
